NAME
     Tags - Structure oriented SGML/XML/HTML/etc. elements manipulation.

STRUCTURE
     Perl structure:

     Reference to array.
     [type, data]

     Types:
     a  - Tag attribute.
     b  - Begin of tag.
     c  - Comment section.
     cd - Cdata section.
     d  - Data section.
     e  - End of tag.
     i  - Instruction section.
     r  - Raw section.

     Data:
     a - $attr, $value
     b - $element
     c - @comment
     cd - @cdata
     d - @data
     e - $element
     i - $target, $code
     r - @raw_data

SEE ALSO
    Task::Tags
        Install the Tags modules.

REPOSITORY
    <https://github.com/michal-josef-spacek/Tags>

